headline: Someone Shared An Airbnb Checkout Chore List Saying, 'One More Reason Why Many Crappy Airbnb's Aren't Doing So Well This Year'
summary: A recent post on X sparked discussion about the current state of Airbnb (NASDAQ:ABNB) that featured a detailed list of checkout chores shared by a guest. “Here is one more reason why many crappy Airbnb's aren't doing so well this year,” the post read, alongside a list of checkout instructions that included tasks like starting the dishwasher, stripping sheets, placing towels in specific baskets, reattaching TV remotes with Velcro, and returning split air unit remotes to their holders.
